<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name=""veiwport" content=""width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Formatters lab!</title>
    </head>
    <body>

        <h1>The formatters lab</h1>
        <p>Welcome to the lab where we style text like scientists style experiments-
        with care and acuracy!each section shows a tag in action!</p>
        
    <h2>Bold v/s strong</h2>
    <p>The <b>cheetah</b> is the fastest animal on land in the whole world!</p>
    <p><strong>always where a helmet</strong> when riding a bicycle.</p>
    
    <h2>Italics v/s Emphasis</h2>
    <p>the scientific name for a red tail catfish is <i>Phractocephalus hemioliopterus</i>.</p>
    <p><em>never ever </em> touch chemicals without wearing gloves!</p>

    <h2>Highlight & small</h2>
    <p>Remember:<mark> water boils at 100°C</mark>at sea level.</p>
    <p>The sun is <small>(approximately)</small> 150km away from earth.</p>

    <h2> deleting text</h2>
    <p>Pluto is a <del>planet</del>a dwarf planet.</p>
    
    <h2>superscript and subscript.</h2>
    <p>the area os a 4*4 square is 16<sup>2</sup></p>
    <p>water is made of H<sub>2</sub>O - 2 hydrogen atoms and 1 oxygen atom.</p>
    
    </body>
</html>